"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-phoebe-gill-olympics-2024-b1172852.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics  A 14-year-old Phoebe Gill stayed up until two in the morning to watchKeely Hodgkinsonrun in the 800metre final at the lastOlympic Games.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 259, \"end\": 265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoebe_Halliwell\", \"score\": 0.8531053690098466, \"rank\": 0.1721881449937531, \"text\": \"Phoebe\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoebe_Halliwell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoebe_Halliwell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, she will be lining up with her in a GB vest after a meteoric rise in middle-distance running for the teenager.\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 498, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 424, \"end\": 426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9994107866041888, \"rank\": 0.0005839913410453694, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gill was crowned British champion last month for the 800m after Hodgkinson, already guaranteed Olympic selection, opted to instead run the 400m at what doubled as the Olympic trials.\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 682, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 517, \"end\": 533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Figure_Skating_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9962368793237674, \"rank\": 0.0037767470365600545, \"text\": \"British champion\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Figure_Skating_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Figure_Skating_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 564, \"end\": 574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.9743087041384182, \"rank\": 0.026368743040341047, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And on the eve of her Olympic debut, Gill said: \\\"Tokyo 2021 was such a memorable watch.\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 733, \"end\": 738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9989428349170955, \"rank\": 0.0010580441791899035, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I stayed up until two in the morning to watch the 800s and watching Keely get that silver was unforgettable.\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To think I am running on this stage is unbelievable.\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 933, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not wait.\\\"\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 950, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gill marked her national title by returning to her old primary school for work experience on the Monday morning.\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 1064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And, having only just finished her first year of A-levels a few weeks ago - she is studying biology, chemistry and maths - almost immediately she headed off to Paris for theTeam GBholding camp before running next week.\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1226, \"end\": 1231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999980550456, \"rank\": 1.9451770794408035e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics 2024: Paris erects ring of steel in bid to thwart threats to security  Olympics 2024: A Games on a spectacular scale - but is Paris ready to party?\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1442, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1301, \"end\": 1306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999980550456, \"rank\": 1.9451770794408035e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1421, \"end\": 1426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999980550456, \"rank\": 1.9451770794408035e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 Olympic Games athletics schedule in full: Events, UK start times and dates  She has not run since the trials, instead opting to be in the stands to watch Hodgkinson break the British record atthe recent London Diamond League.\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1505, \"end\": 1507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9952093641232, \"rank\": 0.004813696471318645, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1609, \"end\": 1619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.9743087041384182, \"rank\": 0.026368743040341047, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 1630, \"end\": 1644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.907956823981593e-14, \"text\": \"British record\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair have talked a few times since the national championships while former Olympic championKelly Holmeshas also been in touch in the wake of her impressive outings on track.\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1859, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Holmes first made contact via a voice message on Instagram, which almost reduced Gill to tears, and Holmes' advice has been to take it all in her stride.\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 2014, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1861, \"end\": 1867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherlock_Holmes\", \"score\": 0.9999999861029211, \"rank\": 1.3897055877115615e-08, \"text\": \"Holmes\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherlock_Holmes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherlock_Holmes\"}, {\"begin\": 1910, \"end\": 1919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.295859750730481e-22, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 1961, \"end\": 1967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherlock_Holmes\", \"score\": 0.9999999861029211, \"rank\": 1.3897055877115615e-08, \"text\": \"Holmes\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherlock_Holmes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherlock_Holmes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As for her target in Paris, at the age of 17 it is understandably relatively low key in terms of expectations.\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2037, \"end\": 2042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999980550456, \"rank\": 1.9451770794408035e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"I definitely want to get everything I can out of it: the village, the atmosphere, being around all these legends of the sport.\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2265, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's easy to say I am coming in with no expectations but I think every athlete always puts some goals in their head.\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2382, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me it's just to progress through as many rounds as possible and to have fun and run with freedom the entire time.\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2502, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know that's when I start to excel, when I am not too stressed out by the environment around me.\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not wait to run with this amazing crowd of people.\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2657, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hopefully it will produce some fast times but let us see what happens.\\\"\", \"from\": 2658, \"to\": 2729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line 